race.comment: BE MY BELLE (3) missed as favourite over this course and distance last time out when jumping the race favourite. Her win here two back was very strong here again and Yuill remains in the saddle. Trending the right way and strikes another very winnable event. TRULY GALLANT (1) dropped back to 1213m last time out and never looked likely, though his run here two back was very impressive. Back up to the mile today is a big tick and the winkers go on too. Drawn awkward but he has the upside to feature in the finish. BLITZ (9) finished off strongly over 1413m here last time out when 1.6L off the winner and getting back up to the mile looks ideal. He'll be back in the run, but if he can finish off in similar fashion today he'll be hard to hold out. BEST RESULT (5) never really looked likely here last start after a good win two back. Can return to form. DAIYAMONDO (8) can improve now third-up into the campaign.
